<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SkyKPI — Precast & AEC Marketing</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Semi+Condensed:wght@300;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" width="40" height="40">
                    <defs>
                        <linearGradient id="g" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                            <stop offset="0" stop-color="#1AB0C4"/>
                            <stop offset="1" stop-color="#1296B0"/>
                        </linearGradient>
                    </defs>
                    <path d="M100,100 L100,47 A53,53 0 0 1 153,100 Z" fill="url(#g)"/>
                    <path d="M100,100 L100,153 A53,53 0 0 1 47,100 Z" fill="url(#g)"/>
                    <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="58" fill="none" stroke="#E8EDF2" stroke-width="6"/>
                    <g stroke="#E8EDF2" stroke-width="6" stroke-linecap="round">
                        <line x1="100" y1="18" x2="100" y2="182"/>
                        <line x1="18" y1="100" x2="182" y2="100"/>
                    </g>
                </svg>
                <span class="wordmark"><span class="sky">Sky</span><span class="kpi">KPI</span></span>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <a href="#services">Services</a>
                <a href="#about">About</a>
                <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Your Precast Producers Get Specified.</h1>
            <p>Spec-stage marketing strategy and content production for precast concrete and AEC. We make you the reference point architects and engineers reach for.</p>
            <a href="#contact" class="cta">Let's Talk</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>What We Do</h2>
            <div class="service-grid">
                <div class="service">
                    <h3>Custom Websites</h3>
                    <p>Fast, modern sites built to rank and convert. Spec-stage positioning baked in.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service">
                    <h3>Social Media & Content</h3>
                    <p>Consistent, credible presence on LinkedIn, Facebook, Instagram. Your stories, our production.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service">
                    <h3>Email & Campaigns</h3>
                    <p>Automated nurture sequences and targeted outreach to architects and engineers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service">
                    <h3>AIA/CE Administration</h3>
                    <p>We manage your AIA CEUs, compliance, and spec-stage positioning with design professionals.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service">
                    <h3>Association Management</h3>
                    <p>Event coordination, member communications, and growth strategy for industry chapters.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="service">
                    <h3>Competitor Monitoring</h3>
                    <p>Know who's winning the spec. Track positioning, messaging, and market moves in real time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About SkyKPI</h2>
            <p>We're a boutique marketing and association management firm based in Frankfort, Illinois. We work exclusively with precast concrete producers and AEC industry associations. We don't do generic marketing. We understand spec-stage positioning, AIA relationships, PCI workflows, and the buyers who actually make decisions in this industry.</p>
            <p>We bring professional camera work, drone content, web development, and ten years of AEC insider knowledge to every project.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Get Specified?</h2>
            <p>Let's talk about what spec-stage positioning looks like for your producers.</p>
            <a href="mailto:hello@skykpi.com" class="cta cta-secondary">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2026 SkyKPI LLC. Frankfort, IL.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
